<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd" identifier="question-32" title="Solución de ecuación lineal simple" adaptive="false" time-dependent="false">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>¿Cuál es la solución de la ecuación <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn></math>?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <span>Incorrecto. Si se reemplaza <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></math> en la ecuación, se obtiene: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#xD7;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>23</mn></math>, que no es igual a <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>7</mn></math>. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></math> no es solución de la ecuación.</span>
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <span>Incorrecto. Si se reemplaza <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></math> en la ecuación, se obtiene: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#xD7;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>13</mn></math>, que no es igual a <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>7</mn></math>. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn></math> no es solución de la ecuación.</span>
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <span>Incorrecto. Si se reemplaza <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math> en la ecuación, se obtiene: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#xD7;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>11</mn></math>, que no es igual a <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>7</mn></math>. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math> no es solución de la ecuación.</span>
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <span>¡Correcto! Si se reemplaza <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math> en la ecuación, se obtiene: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#xD7;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn></math>, que coincide con el lado derecho de la ecuación. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math> es la solución correcta.</span>
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <strong>Resolución paso a paso de la ecuación lineal</strong>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <span>Partimos de la ecuación dada: </span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn>
            </math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>Restamos <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mn>3</mn></math> en ambos lados de la ecuación para dejar el término con <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi></math> solo en un lado:</span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn>
            </math>
            <span>Simplificando, obtenemos:</span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn>
            </math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>Para despejar <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mi>x</mi></math>, dividimos ambos lados de la ecuación por <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math>:</span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mfrac>
                <mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow>
                <mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow>
              </mfrac>
              <mo>=</mo>
              <mfrac>
                <mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow>
                <mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow>
              </mfrac>
            </math>
            <span>Al simplificar, queda:</span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn>
            </math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span>Verificamos la solución reemplazando en la ecuación original:</span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
              <mn>3</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&#xD7;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn>
            </math>
            <span>Como se cumple la igualdad, la solución correcta es </span>
            <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline">
              <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn>
            </math>
            <span>.</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">0</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">0</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">0</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">0</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>